body.text: Click below for more information about the Virtual Assistant:
Students can use the service to search for tutors offering free study sessions to USF students.  Tutors are students that have completed a course and wish to volunteer their knowledge.

Tutors are USF students that volunteer to provide a study sessions which students can sign up for.  Tutors are able to enter which subjects they wish to offer help in, and pick a schedule that works for them.
